org.eclipse.mat.snapshot
Interface SnapshotFactory.Implementation

All Known Implementing Classes:
SnapshotFactoryImpl
Enclosing class:
SnapshotFactory
public static interface SnapshotFactory.Implementation

Describes the snapshot factory implementation. Implemented in the parser plugin. Implementations of this interface need to be registered using the org.eclipse.mat.api.factory extension point.
